    <briefdescription>
<para>The value itself. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The different union fields are provided for convenience, avoiding the need for manual casts. <simplesect kind="note"><para>The array length is of incomplete length on purpose, to facilitate variable length data and because a data length of zero is valid. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para><bold>Important: The integers are little endian!</bold> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
